"'''Republic HoloNet News Core Edition 14:9:04'''" was an in-universe [[HoloNet News (Insider)|Holonet News]] issue published in [[Star Wars Insider 70|''Star Wars Insider'' 70]]. Like the rest of the series, the canonicity of the edition's specific details are no longer confirmed due to the reorganization of the Clone Wars timeline.

